How to lunch ec2 instance in aws?

* go to aws console login with credentials
* Go to console click on ec2
* Step1: Add name 
* step2: Select amazon-linux.6.12 ami free tier
* step3: select by default t3.micro instance type
* step4: create a keypair by rsa and .pem key
* step5: create a network security group or select exsting sgroup
* step6: select by default disk size 8gb
* step7: review and lunch instance

how to connect ec2 into other applications?
like git bash,cmd,putty,mobaxterm

* click on instance go to connect
* select ssh-client id (example-ssh-i) copy and paste in cmd
* ec2-user@ip: sudo -i convert into root user

DEVOPS :-

* Devops combines Development + operation to delivery the software application faster,more relaible,better quality.

Devops Consist of CiCd pipleine,Automation of kuberentes.

Roles & Responbiites :-

* we can manage cloud infrasturcture
* We can Deploy application with their resources
* We can easily moniotr server and virtual server
* Ensure security & performances

Devops phases:-

* Plan
* Code
* Build
* Test
* Operate
* Monitor
* Deployment
* release

